sogou-kaoyan.n: 清单; 目录[出现12次)];围栏; 战场; 赛场[出现0次)]

sogou-gaokao.v: 把…列入; 列举[出现4次)]

1.en: I have added this as a bonus rather than putting it in the list because it seems to me to be more suited to the surrealist genre.
1.cn: 我加上该片作为奖励而不是将它列入排行榜中是因为于我而言该片更适合列为超现实类型。

2.en: Keep your list in your wallet, and pull it out every time you are tempted to trade what you want most in life for what you want this second.
2.cn: 把你的清单放在皮夹中，每次你有要用你人生中最希望得到的东西和此时此刻要得到的作交换时，就把它拿出来。

3.en: Next Actions. This is your immediate, actionable to-do list, a few specific items you've decided to carry out in the next few days.
3.cn: NextActions——这是你即时待办事项，一些你决定在未来数天里要完成的具体的事项。

0.en: This is an impressive list of hobbies.
0.cn: 你的兴趣爱好可真厉害。

1.en: What's next on the list, Peppa? Crisps!
1.cn: 清单上的下一项是什么，佩佩？薯片！

2.cn: 哈密尔·巴卡维。十人名单中的第六个。

3.en: I'm confused, because there's not a list?
3.cn: 好吧，我糊涂了，完全没有清单？

4.en: A signal box, that's on our list, Hooray!
4.cn: 信号盒。我们的清单上面有这个！噢耶！

5.en: Well, I would never leave you off my list.
5.cn: 我决不会把你从我的名单除名。

6.en: It's a short list. Great. I like it. Focus.
6.cn: 那清单非常短。很好，我喜欢，讲重点。

7.en: That just puts us higher on their kill list.
7.cn: 跟他们同盟也许会更危险。

8.en: I can see clouds. Are clouds on the list? No.
8.cn: 我看到了白云。可白云在表格上吗？不在。

9.en: Okay! First thing on my list, get registered.

10.en: Chocolate cake? Chocolate cake? Is that on the list?
10.cn: 巧克力蛋糕？在清单上吗？

11.en: You memorized conjugations for an endless list of verbs.

12.en: Yes. We're very popular. There's a two-year waiting list. Sorry.
12.cn: 是的，这里很受欢迎，预约已经排到2年后，抱歉。

13.en: That's nearly everything on our list. There's one last thing on the list. A plant? Is that on the list?
13.cn: 清单上的东西几乎都有了。清单上还有一种东西。一棵植物？清单上有吗？

14.en: Very good. That's nearly everything on our list. There's one last thing on the list. A plant? Is that on the list?
14.cn: 非常好，清单上的东西几乎都有了。清单上还有一种东西。一棵植物？清单上有吗？

15.en: You wanna be on my list too? Keep talking. Has anyone seem my list by the way?
15.cn: 你想榜上有名就继续说啊，对了，谁有看到我的黑名单？

16.en: Is Granddad dog on the list? Silly Peppa, my Granddad won't be on the list. But he is sailing a boat. And a boat is on the list.
16.cn: 狗爷爷在活动表格上吗？糊涂的佩奇，我的爷爷怎么会在表格上呢。但是他开的一艘船。而一艘船在表格上。

17.en: Go back to the list? He was fine, but I'm not enthused by anyone else on that list.
17.cn: 再看看名单？他还好，但那张名单上别人我都没兴趣。

18.en: Is Granddad dog on the list? Silly Peppa, my granddad won't be on the list. But he is sailing a boat. And a boat is on the list. Hooray!
18.cn: 单子上有狗爷爷吗？笨佩佩，我的狗爷爷不会在清单上的。可是他在划船。而清单上面有船。噢耶！

19.en: A plant? Is that on the list? Oh, no, George. The last thing on the list is fruit. Oh.
19.cn: 一个植物？在清单上吗？噢，不，乔治。清单上最后一项是水果。噢。
